I am Toadere Cristian,a student at CNLR Bistrita, who is trying to learn GitHub and use it for a web development project from now on.

Here, there will be written all ideas and project changes in order to keep track and to be well organised :)

The website will be Formula 1 themed \, with the following content:

1. Driver's Championship

  I. Driver's Standings
    - graphic showing the standing as they are right now
    - progress made over the season
    
  II. A separate page for each driver
    - factual info : best finish, best times, no of diferrent results, parts used, no of season
    - name
    - country
    - team
    - sponsor
    - background story
    - career overview
    - penalty points
    
    
2.Constructor's Championship

  I.  Constructor's Standings
    - graphic showing the standings as they are right now
    - progress made over the season
    
  II. A separate page for each team
    - factual info: titles, race wins, poles, season in sport, results
    - name
    - country/origin
    - engine/PU used
    - drivers
    - sponsors
    - background story
    - history
    - career overview
